      "span_text": "To avoid including unvoiced speech segments, time points at which no fundamental frequency was identified were also removed ͑as the to pitch function steps through the speech signal it assigns time points as either voiced or unvoiced depending on the strength of identified fundamental frequency candidates; for details, see [CITATION_1] ."
